title: The Real Deal
text: This is by far my favorite cologne for spring and summer because of its light, fresh scent. I was very skeptical of this product when I bought it considering the last time I bought this cologne from a department store it was twice the price for a bottle half the size. I was extremely pleasantly surprised when it arrived and it was the same thing! All the people who wrote poor reviews have clearly never used this cologne before because it smells identical, and a small amount is plenty to last the whole day. This is definitely the best deal you‚Äôre going to find for such a high quality fragrance. I couldn‚Äôt recommend buying this product enough!
